				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\hat{R}$$\end{document}R^, efficiency, and auto-correlation of posterior estimates were more reliable for STAN compared to JAGS.

